{"tid":1348303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【南亞文宣】整咗單張，希望南亞朋友唔好被煽動","createTime":"2019-07-22T07:54:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T09:48:55.000Z","uid":273803,"like":71,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"459a15e954be20280e9a7393f0648895f4349ecb","tid":1348303,"uid":273803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:54:16.000Z","msg":"見到網上面有人寫咗唔同語言嘅南亞文宣，呼籲南亞朋友唔好被煽動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我將佢整咗做單張，希望大家可以幫手印出來，貼係多南亞人出沒嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uopVR0r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuopVR0r.png&h=a688f85c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nPDF link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sendspace.com/file/7vnh6v\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sendspace.com%2Ffile%2F7vnh6v&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdRxURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=0c0cfa66\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sendspace.com/file/7vnh6v</a>"},{"pid":"94ebdc3f0e39fcfe79348b8c13386a56ee7ec36d","tid":1348303,"uid":273803,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:54:29.000Z","msg":"Please stay away and decline anyone who pays you to engage in illegal and violent acts. Don&rsquo;t be used. You will be arrested and imprisoned. Your future will be destroyed. The blame will not only be shifted to you but your community. No one can protect you, not even the one who instructed and paid you. Please refrain from violence."},{"pid":"d1560b60e03c570eb61b32d9a83be75db43ef608","tid":1348303,"uid":273803,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:54:39.000Z","msg":"कृपया कसैले तपाइलाई अवैध र हिंसक कार्यमा संग्लग्न हुन प्रोत्साहन गरेमा र भुक्तानी गर्ने बाचा गरेमा अस्विकार गर्नुहोस।आफु बच्नुहोस। यस्ता क्रियाकलापमा संग्लग्न भएमा तपाइलाई गिरफ्तार र कैद गरिनेछ।तपाइको भविष्य नस्ट हुनेछ। दोष केवल तपाइलाई मात्र हैन तपाइको समुदायलाई पनि लाग्नेछ।कसैले पनि तपाइलाई सुरक्च्या गर्नेछैन। तपाइलाई निर्देसन दिएर भुक्तानी गर्ने मानिश्ले पनि तपाइलाई बचाउन सक्ने छैन।त्यहि भएर यस्ता हिंसात्मक क्रियाकलप बाट टाढा रहन आग्रह गरिन्छ।"},{"pid":"1e88f94f2dc572cf7a57be9389b9d59053fc69a9","tid":1348303,"uid":273803,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:54:52.000Z","msg":"Nakikiusap po kami na lumayo kayo at tumanggi sa mga illigal at bayolenteng mga gawain. Wag kayo magpagamit. Masisira lang ang kinabukasan nyo. Ang sisi ay hindi lamang mapupunta sayo, pati na rin sa iyong communidad. Walang makakapag protekta sayo, pati din yung mga nag utos at nag bayad sayo. Pakiusap po, lumayo kayo sa gulo."},{"pid":"e89232167af06c05267b8c2369532b2c9689e1ce","tid":1348303,"uid":273803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:55:05.000Z","msg":"ਕਿਰਪਾ ਕਰਕੇ ਸ਼ਰਾਰਤੀ ਤੱਤਾਂ ਤੋ ਦੂਰ ਰਹੋ ,ਅਤੇ ਨਾਜਾਇਜ਼ ਅਤੇ ਹਿੰਸਕ ਕੰਮ ਕਰਨ ਲਈ ਤੁਹਾਨੂੰ ਅਦਾਇਗੀ ਕਰਨ ਵਾਲੇ ਕਿਸੇ ਵੀ ਵਿਅਕਤੀ ਨੂੰ ਇਨਕਾਰ ਕਰੋ। ਤੁਹਾਨੂੰ ਗ੍ਰਿਫਤਾਰ ਕੀਤਾ ਜਾ ਸਕਾਦਾ ਹੈ ਅਤੇ ਕੈਦ ਵੀ ਕੀਤਾ ਜਾ ਸਕਦਾ ਹੈ।ਤੁਹਾਡੇ ਭਵਿੱਖ ਤਬਾਹ ਹੋ ਜਾਵੇਗਾ। ਦੋਸ਼ ਸਿਰਫ ਤੁਹਾਡੇ ਤੇ ਨਹੀਂ ਪਰ ਪੂਰੇ ਸਮੁਦਾਏ ਤੇ ਆਏਗਾ। ਇੱਥੋਂ ਤਕ ਕਿ ਉਹ ਵੀ ਜਿਸ ਨੇ ਤੁਹਾਨੂੰ ਹਿਦਾਇਤ ਦਿੱਤੀ ਹੈ ਅਤੇ ਅਦਾਇਗੀ ਕੀਤੀ ਹੈ। ਕ੍ਰਿਪਾ ਕਰਕੇ ਹਿੰਸਾ ਤੋਂ ਦੂਰ ਰਹੋ।"},{"pid":"b3fdd5ea2edbb40f2e40d4d8a7548c298a428a2a","tid":1348303,"uid":273803,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:55:34.000Z","msg":"推到UST南亞仔同VTC南亞仔入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b452d9dd01a5515fe02dd84fce17cf7d80b4398","tid":1348303,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3fdd5ea2edbb40f2e40d4d8a7548c298a428a2a","tid":1348303,"uid":273803,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:55:34.000Z","msg":"推到UST南亞仔同VTC南亞仔入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:56:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81eaff64866026f7a6b4da2088e08e3718e3f5e1","tid":1348303,"uid":42135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT